Package: samesies
Title: Measure Similarity Across Text, Factors, or Numbers
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "dylanpieper@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Samesies is a reliability tool for comparing lists of texts, factors, or numerical values 
    to measure their similarity. The package's motivating use case is evaluating the consistency of 
    Large Language Model (LLM) responses across models, providers, or prompts.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
